{"id":232473163,"title":"Aesop Tacit 悟香水","content":"https://i.imgur.com/v96hQlN.jpg\n在繁雜的思緒，\n我們要有沈澱的體悟。\n\n揮灑香水的前調，\n是活力很滿的柑橘香氣，\n過一陣子慢慢飄出羅勒的草味，\n很像來到毫無邊界的草原，\n最後岩蘭草的氣息，\n把所有的思緒，緩緩的沈澱。\n\n櫃姐推薦如果心情混亂，\n將香水噴入原香水紙盒，\n淡淡的輕聞可以讓自己心情沈澱下來。\n\n整體而言，\n持香度比JM好很多，\n適合一年四季的好穿搭，\n瓶身設計簡潔，\n也適合與JM混香，\n喜歡與羅勒與橙花搭配，增加清新感。","excerpt":"在繁雜的思緒，我們要有沈澱的體悟。揮灑香水的前調，是活力很滿的柑橘香氣，過一陣子慢慢飄出羅勒的草味，很像來到毫無邊界的草原，最後岩蘭草的氣息，把所有的思緒，緩緩的沈澱。櫃姐推薦如果心情混亂，將香水噴入","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"1a14ba93-3989-47e5-aedc-a3918963100e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-10T05:00:40.739Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-10T23:32:19.584Z","commentCount":16,"likeCount":98,"tags":[],"topics":["香水"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"香氛","forumAlias":"fragrance","school":"國立彰化師範大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":97},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/v96hQlN.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"88c26970-8c24-4b0c-9f26-7f95838a1754","url":"https://i.imgur.com/v96hQlNl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/v96hQlNl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/v96hQlNl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-10T05:00:40.739Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-10T23:32:19.584Z"},{"id":"88c26970-8c24-4b0c-9f26-7f95838a1754","url":"https://i.imgur.com/v96hQlN.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/v96hQlN","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/v96hQlNl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-10T05:00:40.739Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-10T23:32:19.584Z"}],"postAvatar":""}